PrecisAmendments to the TOBACCO REGULATIONS which will require that domestic cigarettes and fine-cut tobacco destined for export be marked "Not for sale in Canada" and that both domestic and imported tobacco products intended for the domestic "duty-free" market be marked "Duty not paid - Canada".
